  dialogueLines:
  - The amount of fish you need to catch for each area of the Dogfish Run is shown
    in the top right of the screen.
  - When you catch enough, the portal to the next area will open and you can continue
    on your journey!
  - Unfortunately, I can't go with you young Fin, my work is elsewhere...
  - Good Luck! And always remember ........ you are your father's son!
